---
title: Moroccan-Style Chickpea Bowl with Pickled Radish, Garlic Dip & Tortilla Chips
description: When you simmer hearty chickpeas with subtly sweet veggies, garlicky tomatoes and a rich chermoula-spiced sauce, the result is pretty magical. Serve with a quick pickled radish for a touch of tang, a garlic dip for creaminess and oven-baked tortilla chips for crunch and scooping!
